Caring Times and Chapel Craft are owned and operated by Mark Thomas Co. 
				Chapel Craft is unique: combined with Mark Thomas, it is the only manufacturer of crosses and crucifixes for the funeral trade to sell directly to funeral directors. 

Mark Thomas Co. sells exclusively to funeral homes. We do not sell to the general public.














 















 












 






























