Micro-perfed Prayer Cards











All our Prayer Cards are sold on 8-up, 8 1/2" x 11" micro-perfed sheets. There are 125 sheets, or 1,000
cards, in a package. Individual cards measure 2 1/2" x 4 1/4". (3202 fold-over
cards are packed in 500s; card size is 5" x 4 1/4".)

Prayer cards
are blank on the back, and are designed to be personalized with a copier, computer
printer or offset press.

Styles may be assorted and combined with
orders for acknowledgments and memorial folders for quantity pricing. There
is no minimum order on prayer cards. We will open packages and ship you the quantity
you need. We also sell blank prayer card stock.

Free Prayer Card Templates
Free Prayer Card & Bookmark Sample Binder

We now offer free prayer card templates on our web-site.  Click on Templates in the menu bar to access the template page.
We have put together a Prayer Card & Bookmark Sample Binder that makes it easy for you to keep our complete line of products at your fingertips.

Our
Prayer Card & Bookmark Sample Binder has all our prayer cards and bookmarks in sheet protectors, organized in a three-ring binder with a full-color cover. It's a great tool for you to use in showing the prayer cards and bookmarks you offer to your families. Plus, it's easy to add our new prayer cards and bookmarks as we publish new designs. We ought to charge for this, but so far it's free. Call and we'll send you one.

								
If you have one of our Prayer Card & Bookmark Sample Binders, it should have all the prayer cards and bookmarks shown on this web site. If you are missing any, please call us at 1-800-437-2635 so we can furnish the missing ones.

Free Replacement Binder. With all our new prayer cards and bookmarks, your old binder may be too small. We will happily send out a larger replacement at no charge on request. Just call us at 1-800-437-2635.














